INSERT INTO `noticeentity` VALUES (1,'<p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.93px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(34, 34, 40);\">안녕하세요.&nbsp; 구슬구슬입니다.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.93px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(34, 34, 40);\">개인정보 보호를 위해 아래와 같이 개인정보 처리방침이 2022년 10월 21일부로 일부 개정되었습니다.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.93px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(34, 34, 40);\">이에 개정된 주요 내용을 안내 드리오니,</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.93px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(34, 34, 40);\">회원 여러분께서는 변경되는 내용을 확인하여 주시기를 당부드립니다.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.93px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(34, 34, 40);\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.93px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(34, 34, 40);\">1. 개정 주요 사유</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.93px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(34, 34, 40);\">&nbsp; - 개인정보 보호법 준수를 위해 개인정보 수집 · 이용 중인 항목을 누락없이 고지하고,</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: collapse; border: 0px; font-family: &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, sans-serif; letter-spacing: -0.93px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(34, 34, 40);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;일반인이 이해할 수 있도록 쉽고 명확하게 처리방침을 개선하였습니다.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 10px; border-spacing: 0px; border-collapse: c